LILLIAN BECKER, PROSECUTRIX, v. NATHAN ROSENFELD, JUSTICE OF THE PEACE, DEFENDANT. Argued January 21, 1931 Decided February 6, 1931.

Before Justices Pakkek, Campbell and Bodine.

Eor the prosecutrix, Kass & Eass. Pee Ctjkiam.

The conviction was not returned with the writ.

The writ will therefore be dismissed.
